flag_description: Enable multi-agent routing system - routes requests through ORC to specialist agents
Enable Orchestrator Agent - central routing and response synthesis
Enable Analytics & Forecasting Agent - projections and scenario modeling
Enable Audience Intelligence Agent - segmentation and targeting
Enable Channel Strategy Agent - channel mix and allocation
Enable Supply Path Optimization Agent - fee analysis and partner evaluation
Enable Document Generation Agent - plan and brief generation
Enable Performance Intelligence Agent - optimization and anomaly detection
Enable verbose logging for all routing decisions and agent communications
Fall back to MPA v5.5 monolithic agent on multi-agent errors
Allow ORC to route to multiple specialists in parallel when applicable
Enable A/B testing between multi-agent and monolithic MPA
Percentage of traffic routed to multi-agent system during A/B test
